are long-stay hospitals). In this paragraph, references to HMOs and CMPs must be read as applicable also to HCPPs that
furnish inpatient services in acute care hospitals. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Criteria for reasonableness. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
