<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Required information. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
The required information is any information that HCFA identifies as necessary for it to evaluate whether the HMO or
CMP qualifies for an exception to the presumptive limit. It may include, but is not limited to, data on costs of services
furnished to individual enrollees, documenting the volume and intensity of services required by the Medicare enrollees.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(iii) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Consequences of failure to provide required information. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
