the HMO or CMP meets the conditions for additional payments, and gives the HMO or CMP notice of that determination.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(8) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
