<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
An organization wishing to participate as an HCPP must_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) Enter into a written agreement with HCFA as specified in &sect;417.801; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
