from the reasonable cost actually incurred by the HCPP_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(A) An amount equal to 20 percent of the incurred cost, representing the Medicare coinsurance; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(B) The actuarial value of the part B deductible. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
