to deny payments to an individual or to the provider that furnished services to the individual. The PRO performs reconsideration
of cases in which it made a determination subject to reconsideration. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(e) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
