in its agreement. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(g) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Dual intermediary responsibilities.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 With respect to the responsibility for service to provider-based HHAs and provider-based hospices, where the HHA
or hospice and its parent provider will be served by different intermediaries under &sect;421.117 of this part, the
designated regional intermediary will process bills, make coverage determinations and make payments to the HHAs
and hospices. The intermediary serving the parent provider will perform all fiscal functions, including audits
and settlement of the Medicare cost reports and the HHA and hospice supplement worksheets. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

