<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) Furnished to Medicare beneficiaries; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Covered under Medicare; and 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(iii) In accordance with PRO determinations when they are services for which the PRO has assumed review responsibility
under its contract with HCFA. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) The intermediary takes appropriate action to reject or adjust the claim if_
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) The intermediary or the PRO determines that the services furnished were not reasonable, not medically necessary,
or not furnished in the most appropriate setting; or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) The intermediary determines that the claim does not properly reflect the kind and amount of services furnished.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
