public hearing will be held on the proposed threatened status for the flat-tailed horned lizard (
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=3 -->
Phrynosoma mcallii
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=10 g=1 f=1 -->
). At the hearing, the Service will allow all interested parties to submit oral or written comments on the proposal.
The public comment period is extended to provide the public with more time to comment.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG QTAG 02 -->
<!-- PJG /QTAG -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

